section_title: Issues relating to greenhouse gas inventories
sentences: Helen Plume (New Zealand) reported on the informal consultations.

SBSTA adopted the conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.17) without amendment. Issues relating to Protocol Articles 7 (communication of information) and 8 (review of information): Murray Ward (New Zealand) reported on informal consultations.
SBSTA agreed on conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.30) and forwarded the draft decision to the COP (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.30/Add.1).
enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
